  "prompt": "What are the signs that a Taurus man really likes you?",
  "response": "Taurus men are known for being slow and steady, but also very genuine and loyal. It can be a little tricky to tell if they like you because they're not usually overly demonstrative. However, there are definite signs to look for:\n\n**Key Signs of Interest (Taurus Style):**\n\n*   **He Spends Quality Time With You:** This is HUGE. Taurus men value their time and comfort. If he's consistently making an effort to hang out with you, even if it's just chilling and watching a movie, that's a big indicator. He's choosing to spend his precious downtime with *you*.\n*   **He's Attentive and Present:** When you're talking, he's *really* listening. He makes eye contact, remembers details you've told him, and asks follow-up questions. He's engaged in the conversation and genuinely cares about what you have to say.\n*   **Physical Touch (Even Subtle):** Taurus men are sensual beings. Look for subtle touches: a light touch on your arm, a lingering hug, a playful bump of shoulders. If he's comfortable enough to break the physical barrier, it's a good sign.\n*   **He Shares His Food and Resources:** A classic Taurus move. Offering you a bite of his food, sharing his favorite snacks, or lending you something important to him shows he wants to take care of you and share his world. This is a sign of generosity and care.\n*   **He Opens Up Emotionally (Eventually):** Taurus men can be reserved, especially at first. If he starts to share his feelings, vulnerabilities, or personal stories with you, it means he trusts you and sees you as someone he can confide in. Don't expect this right away; it takes time to build trust.\n*   **He Remembers Important Dates/Details:** He remembers your birthday, your favorite color, or that you have a big presentation coming up. This shows he's paying attention and cares about the things that matter to you.\n*   **He Introduces You to His Inner Circle:** Taurus men are fiercely loyal to their friends and family. If he introduces you to them, it means he sees you as someone special and wants you to be a part of his life.\n*   **He Does Thoughtful Things for You:** He might bring you a coffee, help you with a task, or offer to drive you somewhere. These small acts of service show that he's thinking about you and wants to make your life easier.\n*   **He Tries to Make You Comfortable:** Taurus men are all about comfort and security. If he's always making sure you're comfortable, whether it's offering you a blanket, pulling out your chair, or making sure you have everything you need, it's a sign he cares about your well-being.\n*   **He Gives You Gifts (Especially Practical Ones):** Taurus men are practical. While they might give you something romantic, they're also likely to give you something useful that they know you'll appreciate.\n*   **He's Patient and Understanding:** He's not demanding or pushy. He understands that you might need time to warm up and he's willing to wait. He's supportive and encouraging, and he accepts you for who you are.\n*   **He Expresses His Admiration:** While he may not say \"I love you\" early on, he might compliment you on your appearance, your intelligence, or your kindness. He'll find ways to let you know that he appreciates you.\n\n**Important Considerations:**\n\n*   **Patience is Key:** Taurus men are not known for rushing into things. Be patient and give him time to open up and show you how he feels.\n*   **Create a Comfortable Atmosphere:** Taurus men are drawn to people who are genuine, down-to-earth, and create a sense of stability.\n*   **Appreciate the Simple Things:** Taurus men value the simple pleasures in life. Enjoying a good meal together, taking a walk in nature, or just relaxing at home can be a great way to connect with him.\n*   **Be Loyal and Trustworthy:** Loyalty is incredibly important to Taurus men. If you want to win his heart, show him that you're someone he can rely on.\n*   **Don't Play Games:** Taurus men appreciate honesty and sincerity. Playing games or trying to manipulate him will only push him away.\n\nIf you're seeing several of these signs, chances are a Taurus man is genuinely interested in you. Remember to be yourself, be patient, and enjoy the journey. Good luck!\n",
